    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate your way through a vibrant hexagonal grid in <i>Hexa Path</i>, a relaxing yet challenging puzzle game. Take control of the blue ship and capture every tile on the board by filling them with your color. Sounds simple? Think again! Each level introduces new obstacles and mechanics, testing both your strategy and problem-solving skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hexagonal Grid Gameplay</strong>: Move across hexagonal tiles, filling them with blue to complete each puzzle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Mechanics</strong>: Numbered tiles require multiple passes, while lettered tiles must be captured in sequence. Teleport between green tiles, and neutralize enemy ships by stepping on them before they block your path!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enemies and Obstacles</strong>: Watch out for enemy ships that are trying to trap you. Plan carefully, or restart the level if you get stuck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60 Puzzles</strong>: With 60 diverse levels, experience increasing difficulty and intricate puzzle designs that will make you think.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Experience</strong>: Immerse yourself in simple, minimalist visuals and an atmospheric soundtrack, perfect for a relaxing puzzle-solving session.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're seeking a casual game for a quick challenge or a strategic puzzle to unwind, <i>Hexa Path</i> delivers a satisfying and engaging experience for all types of players. With its intuitive mouse controls and unique grid mechanics, it's the perfect game for puzzle enthusiasts. Ready to fill the hexes and solve the path?</p>",
